ages/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jonathan Knowles</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Zain Vawda</em></p> <p>Oil prices are holding steady near the $72.35 support level, staying in a 6-day period of little movement. OPEC+ meets on Thursday, and there\u2019s a higher chance they will extend their oil output cuts to Q1 2025.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741849-opec-plus-meeting-in-focus-will-oil-production-cuts-continue-through-march-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:56:00"}, {"id": "4741816", "title": "The Children's Place: The Turnaround Hiccup", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business on Wall Street in Manhattan\" data-id=\"1220627489\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6240px\" height=\"4160px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Pgiam/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>The Children's Place, Inc.</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PLCE\" title=\"The Children's Place, Inc.\">PLCE</a></span>) is a retailer that has been in an extremely volatile trade. We called for a rapid-return buy at $9 in September. The stock more than doubled in a few sessions. However, the stock has</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741816-the-childrens-place-the-turnaround-hiccup", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:41:25"}, {"id": "4741815", "title": "Property Type Round-Up From REITworld 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Drone Shot of Las Vegas Strip at Nightfall\" data-id=\"1808874665\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"810px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">halbergman</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>We recently attended the annual REITWorld conference, where we conducted 33 meetings with REIT CEOs and CFOs. We also attended two organized dinners, three property tours, and a run around the Las Vegas strip with a REIT management team to maximize our</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741815-property-type-round-up-from-reitworld-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:41:01"}, {"id": "4741814", "title": "AMD: Positioned For Takeoff As 2025 Demand Gains Momentum", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Abstract circuit board with a lot of micro chips\" data-id=\"1397047849\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">sankai</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The recent pullback in <b>Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMD\" title=\"Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.\">AMD</a></span>) stock following its <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4220849-advanced-micro-devices-non-gaap-eps-of-0_92-in-line-revenue-of-6_82m-misses-6_7b\">Q3 2024 earnings report</a> presents what, I believe, is a Dip-Buy opportunity for long-term investors. Because of AMD's accelerating momentum in the artificial intelligence and data</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s